name: プロデューサー
text:
おめでとう、甘奈
宣言通り、実力を十分に発揮できてたな
trans:
Congratulations, Amana. Just like you said earlier,
you really brought out everything you've learned.

name: 甘奈
text:
えっへへー、ありがとープロデューサーさん☆
甘奈、頑張っちゃった
trans:
Ehehe～ Thanks so much, Producer-san☆
I really gave it my absolute best out there.

name: 甘奈
text: プロデューサーさんの応援のおかげかも！
trans:
But winning was really thanks to your support,
Producer-san!

name: プロデューサー
text:
だったら嬉しいけどな
でも、これは甘奈の実力だよ
trans:
If you see it that way, it makes me happy.
But honestly, Amana, this victory is all because of
your skill.

name: 甘奈
text:
じゃあ、この先も実力に見合った活躍ができるように
めーっちゃ頑張らなきゃだね！
trans:
If that's the case, then I'm going to work even 
harder from now on to make sure my performances
match my abilities!
